      <title>德国林德纳表示无需进一步承担欧洲债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/germany-s-lindner-says-no-need-for-further-european-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，在各国财务状况恢复正常之前，欧盟不应为进一步的项目提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/germany-s-lindner-says-no-need-for-further-european-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:31:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于生产问题和天气影响煤炭销售，皮博迪股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/peabody-slumps-as-production-issues-weather-crimp-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大煤矿公司皮博迪能源公司(Peabody Energy Corp.)警告称，由于澳大利亚煤矿生产问题和美国需求疲软，第一季度销售额将低于预期，该公司股价跌至七个月以来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/peabody-slumps-as-production-issues-weather-crimp-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行维持利率不变并表示六月份首次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-interest-rates-and-firms-path-to-first-cut-in-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行第五次会议维持利率不变，同时发出迄今为止最明确的信号，即通胀降温将很快允许其开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-interest-rates-and-firms-path-to-first-cut-in-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴斯夫因考虑裁员电池材料工厂而股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/basf-may-cut-all-jobs-at-battery-materials-plant-over-red-tape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴斯夫股票下跌，此前该化学品公司表示正在考虑解雇其芬兰电池材料工厂的所有工人，该工厂多年来一直因繁文缛节和环保组织的反对而受阻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/basf-may-cut-all-jobs-at-battery-materials-plant-over-red-tape</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:24:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
